          ></small
        >
        <br />
        <img src="/img/webp/logo.webp" alt="SunflowerDM Logo" class="logo" />
      </header>
      <main>
        <aside class="instructions-container container">
          <div class="instructions">
            <p>
              <strong>INSTRUCTIONS:</strong> Choose a season and region to
              generate a travel narrative for your players. Optionally include
              combat and non-combat encounters.
              <span
                class="tooltip"
                title="Sign in to save and retrieve responses for up to 24 hours."
              >
